#360 Implement Multi-Signature Admin Operations
Repo Avatar
Xoulomon/Scavenger
Labels: enhancement, smart-contract, security
Priority: High
Estimated Effort: 10-15 hours

Description:
Add multi-signature requirement for critical admin operations (transfer admin, set percentages, deactivate waste). Require M-of-N admin approvals.

Acceptance Criteria:

 Add AdminProposal struct with proposal ID, action, approvers
 Add propose_admin_action(action) function
 Add approve_admin_proposal(proposal_id) function
 Add execute_admin_proposal(proposal_id) function
 Configurable threshold (e.g., 2-of-3)
 Proposal expiration after 7 days
 Emit ProposalCreated, ProposalApproved, ProposalExecuted events
 15+ comprehensive tests
Technical Details:

Store proposals in Map
Use bitflags or Vec for approver tracking
Consider gas costs for proposal storage

